=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2528721\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 13, 2022</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104ivb1665702925150.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ivb1665702925150.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ivb1665702925150.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"ivb1665702925150\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Test Load Balancing with Web server and Tomcat\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body taskbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">\n</p>\n<section><ol class=\"ol steps\"><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"ivb1665702925150__li_d23249e1_d23250e1_d23251e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">Start the Web server (Apache or IIS) you configured to work with Tomcat .\n </span>\n</li><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"ivb1665702925150__li_d23252e1_d23253e1_d23254e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">Start two Tomcat servers configured as described in <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"exu1665702924873.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/exu1665702924873.html\" title=\"You can install two or more Tomcat servers, either on one machine or on different machines. If you install on one machine, you can define the default host as localhost.\">Configure Multiple Tomcat Servers</a>.\n </span>\n</li><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"ivb1665702925150__li_d23255e1_d23256e1_d23257e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">Start two Uniface Routers from two separate Uniface installations, either on the same machine or on different machines.\n </span>\n</li><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"ivb1665702925150__li_d23258e1_d23259e1_d23260e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\" id=\"ivb1665702925150__p_d46673e1_d46674e1_d46675e1\">Open one browser and enter the WRD URL to run a test page, for example:\n <code class=\"ph codeph\">http://localhost:8080/uniface/wrd/sptest</code>\n</span>\n<div class=\"itemgroup info\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ivb1665702925150__p_d46676e1_d46677e1_d46678e1\">The Uniface server page test1 from Tomcat server 1 should be displayed.</p>\n</div>\n</li><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"ivb1665702925150__li_d23261e1_d23262e1_d23263e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">Click the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Reload</span> button several times. The same test1 page should be displayed each time.\n </span>\n</li><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"ivb1665702925150__li_d23264e1_d23265e1_d23266e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\" id=\"ivb1665702925150__p_d46679e1_d46680e1_d46681e1\">Open another browser and enter the WRD URL to run a test page, for example:\n <code class=\"ph codeph\">http://localhost:8080/uniface/wrd/sptest</code>\n</span>\n<div class=\"itemgroup info\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ivb1665702925150__p_d46682e1_d46683e1_d46684e1\">The Uniface server page test2 from Tomcat server 2 should be displayed.</p>\n</div>\n</li><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"ivb1665702925150__li_d23267e1_d23268e1_d23269e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\">Click the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Reload</span> button several times. The same test2 page from should be displayed each time.\n </span>\n</li><li class=\"li step stepexpand\" id=\"ivb1665702925150__li_d23270e1_d23271e1_d23272e1\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\" id=\"ivb1665702925150__p_d46685e1_d46686e1_d46687e1\">Open a third browser an enter the WRD URL to run a test page, for example:\n <code class=\"ph codeph\">http://localhost:8080/uniface/sptest</code>\n</span>\n<div class=\"itemgroup info\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ivb1665702925150__p_d46688e1_d46689e1_d46690e1\">The Uniface server page test1 from Tomcat1 should be displayed. This indicates that the load balancing is working correctly.</p>\n</div>\n</li></ol></section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528721\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528721\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Test Load Balancing with Web server and Tomcat Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 13, 2022 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Test Load Balancing with Web server and Tomcat Start the Web server (Apache or IIS) you configured to work with Tomcat . Start two Tomcat servers configured as described in Configure Multiple Tomcat Servers . Start two Uniface Routers from two separate Uniface installations, either on the same machine or on different machines. Open one browser and enter the WRD URL to run a test page, for example: http://localhost:8080/uniface/wrd/sptest The Uniface server page test1 from Tomcat server 1 should be displayed. Click the Reload button several times. The same test1 page should be displayed each time. Open another browser and enter the WRD URL to run a test page, for example: http://localhost:8080/uniface/wrd/sptest The Uniface server page test2 from Tomcat server 2 should be displayed. Click the Reload button several times. The same test2 page from should be displayed each time. Open a third browser an enter the WRD URL to run a test page, for example: http://localhost:8080/uniface/sptest The Uniface server page test1 from Tomcat1 should be displayed. This indicates that the load balancing is working correctly. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}